hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[804] 係堅尼地城/西環有需要落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc28ba0d0a80fc3d0085c907ac153052ca6aab7","tid":1396143,"uid":113630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"請大家炸銀龍Facebook逼佢哋回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nganlung.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnganlung.hk&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=6373168f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nganlung.hk</a>"}]}